descrShort: The file path of the XML test file
The time when the current test is started
The time when the previous test is terminating (? character means that it is not sure because test is in progress)
The time duration of the previous test (in sec) (? character means that it is not sure because test is in progress)
The time when the report is generated
The time duration from the current test beginning when the report is generated in seconds
The time interval for the graph drawing and CSV file writing in seconds
Number of complete test runs (which is now terminated including OK and KO run)
Number/flow of failed (KO) test runs (which is completed with a failure)
The time duration of the test runs in seconds
